      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Woj man bij Wehrschu\nGaltu ehſt/ un Ahschu Affini\ndſert?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Uppure Deewann Pateiſ-\nſchanu/ un maſfa tam wiſfu-\naugſtakam tawu Apfohlifchann.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un peefauz mann Behdu\nLaikâ/ tad es tevi gribbu ts-\nraut/ un tew buhs mann goh-\nDaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ug to BesDeetvigu\nfakka Deews : Ka drihkſti tu\nmannus Liffimus dandſinaht/\nun neumm mannü Derribu tawá\nMutte.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kur tu tomehr Bahrmah-\ngifchann eenihſti/ un mett man-\nnus Wahrdus pahr Galwn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad tu weenu Sagli re-\ndſi/ tad tezz tu ar winnu/ un\ntew irr Dalliba ar teim Laulibas\nBahrkahpajeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu dohdees ar tawu\nMutti us Launu/ untawa Nieh-\nle Wiltibu dsenn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu fehd prett tawa\nBrahta ruunadains/ tawas\nMahtes Dehln tu iſfunni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "To darri tu/un eszeeſchu\nkluffu/ tad tu dohma/ ka es ta\npatt buſchu ka tu/ bet es pahr-\nmahzifchu tew/ un turreſchu tew\nto preekſch Azzim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Saprohteet jelle to/ kaſ\njuhs Deewu aiſmirſtat/ ka es\neekſch ne faplohsu/ un Jsglah-\nbeja neward.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ras Pateiſchann uypu-\nre/ tas turr mann Gohdá/ un\ntas irr tas Zettch/ ka es taim to\nDeewa Peſtifchann parahdiſchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta LI. Dseefma.\nIrr weena janha un kraſchna Dseefma no\nAtgreeſchanas no Grekkeem/ eckſch ka Dah-\nwids luhs/ ka Deers winna Grehkus grih-\nbetu veedoht/ fo winſch Laulibu pahrkahp-\ndams un nokaudams darrijs : 1. Jo tas\nirr winnam no Sirds schehl : 5/6. Wiſch\nluhds arridsan/ ka Deews to Swehta Garra\nKlahtſiahweſchanu eekſch winna gribbetu\nwairoht : 12. Un winna Walſtibu un to\nkriſtitu Draudſi usturreht : 20.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eena Dahwida Dseef-\nima/ preeſch ta angsta\nDseedataja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tas Braweets Nah-\ntans pee winna nahzis/ kad\nwinſch bija pee Batſebas ee-\ngahjis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Apschehlojees pahr mannim\naf Deews! pehz tawas Scheh-\nlaſtibas/ isdelde mannas Bahr-\nkahpfchanas pehz tawas leelas\nSirds Schehlaſtibas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Masga mann labbi no\nmannas Noseedsibas/ un fchih-\nſti mannü no manneem Grehkeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo es atſihſtu mannü\nBahrkahpfchanu/ un mannü\nGrehki irr weenumehr manná\nPreeſcha.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tew weenam efimu es greh-\nkojs/ un Launa preeſch tawahm\nAzzim darrijs/ ka tu eekſch ta-\nweem Wahrdem taijus/ un\ntawas Teetas fchihſts\npaleezi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rangi/ es efimu eekſch\nTttttt No-\n"
    }
  ],
